Profit Funds Investment Trust - The Profit Fund: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 22, 2017 10:47 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Profit Funds Investment Trust - The Profit Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
As of September 28, 2016, Profit Funds Investment Trust - The Profit Fund has gone out of business. Profit Funds Investment Trust - The Profit Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Profit Investment Management, LLC. The fund invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in dividend-paying value stocks of large-cap companies having market capitalization exceeding $10 billion. It employs fundamental analysis by focusing on factors such as low price/earnings ratios relative to a company’s sector or historical performance, strong balance sheet ratios, high return on ca...
As of September 28, 2016, Profit Funds Investment Trust - The Profit Fund has gone out of business. Profit Funds Investment Trust - The Profit Fund is an open-ended equity mutual fund launched and managed by Profit Investment Management, LLC. The fund invests in the public equity markets of the United States. It invests in stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. The fund invests in dividend-paying value stocks of large-cap companies having market capitalization exceeding $10 billion. It employs fundamental analysis by focusing on factors such as low price/earnings ratios relative to a company’s sector or historical performance, strong balance sheet ratios, high return on capital, low price/earnings growth ratios relative to a company’s sector, and political, economic, or other events could affect the company’s performance to create its portfolio. The fund benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the S&P 500 Index. It was formerly known as Profit Funds Investment Trust - Profit Value Fund. Profit Funds Investment Trust - The Profit Fund was formed on November 15, 1996 and is domiciled in the United States.
Detailed Description


6701 Democracy BoulevardSuite 300Bethesda, MD 20817United StatesFounded in 1996



Phone: 301-650-0059

Fax: 301-650-0608








Key Executives for Profit Funds Investment Trust - The Profit Fund


Profit Funds Investment Trust - The Profit Fund does not have any Key Executives recorded. 





